			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I agreed HGs are the same level range in zones you find them.   At lv35 the Hill and Sand Giants coned blue, even or yellow and not only can you solo them but I got all of lv 35 doing so and on the new server where nobody is twinked yet.
<br />

<br />
Start by getting SOW potions or JBoots (at lv 35 it is easy to solo the AC in SRo as well as the Shadowmen).  Cast a focused earth pet then give him BO2 and a fire shield; armor and swords didn't seem to make much difference.  Pull with Malaise, send pet, then get way back to where only your Cinder Bolt is in range.  At the correct distance the giant will look like it's not moving and the pet will never loose agro.  Chain cast bolts at him until dead.  Blue cons and usualy even cons would die with some health left on the pet.  Yellow cons would generaly kill the pet but as the giant would be rooted and far away it is possible to get off one or two more bolts to finish.  
<br />

<br />
Not great exp as there are long downtimes but a nice challenge and good loot.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
